@Hickory.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5291

### Health Check
GET {{Hickory.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Get All Service Requests
GET {{Hickory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/servicerequests
Accept: application/json

### Get Service Request by ID
GET {{Hickory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/servicerequests/1
Accept: application/json

### Create New Service Request
POST {{Hickory.Api_HostAddress}}/api/servicerequests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe",
  "phone": "555-9999",
  "address": "777 Hickory Lane",
  "serviceType": "Irrigation",
  "description": "Sprinkler zone 2 not turning on."
}

### Weather Forecast (Default Example)
GET {{Hickory.Api_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json
